	(text_box "Overall Architecture\n-------------------------\n\nRaspberry Pico 2 (RP2350)\n\n- 32 (Buttons) + 8 (Fader) WS2812B -> PIO (1 gpio)\n- 8 Rotary Encoder -> MCP23017 (I2C)\n- 32 Buttons + 8 Encoder-Button -> MCP23017 (I2C)\n- 8 ALPS Motorfader: Value Input -> MCP3208 (SPI)\n- 8 ALPS Motorfader: Motor Control -> 4xTB6612FNG / PWM (GPIO), IN1/IN2 (MCP23017)"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
